CurriculumVitae

&nbsp;

ZILONGLI

Professor,ZhejiangUniversityofPRChina

PhD,KobeUniversityofJapan,March2002

AvisitingscientistinHarvardUniversity(Nov.2006-June2008)

PermanentAddress:Dept.ofEarthSciences,ZhejiangUniversity,Hangzhou310027,China&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;

&nbsp;

1.RESEARCHINTERESTS:

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mainlyfocusingontheformationoftheorogenicbeltanditsmineralization.

(1)Petrology,geochemistry,geochronologyandpetrogenesisofthePermianlargeigneousprovinceinTarimBasinofNWChinaaswellasgeneticrelationwithmantleplumeandcrust-mantleinteraction;

(2)Metamorphismandgeodynamicevolutionofbasicgranulitesandultrahigh-temperaturegarnet-sillimanite-spinel-orthopyroxenegranulite(UHT)inChinaSouthAltayorogenicbelt;

(3)PetrologyandgeochemistryanddynamicsoftheYanshaniangranitoidsandmafic-ultramafic&nbsp;rocks,(ultra)high-pressuremetamorphicrocks(UHP)&nbsp;anditsmineralizationofAu-Ag-Cu-Pb-ZninSouthChinaandEastAsia;

(4)Understandingmetamorpho-magmaticprocessesandtectonicevolutionofArchean-ProterozoicNorthChinacraton.

Morerecently,as&nbsp;areviewerofgeologicalexpertofPRChinatoattendanevaluationprocessesoftheYandangshanGlobalGeopark(ZhejiangProvinceofPRChina).

&nbsp;

